Package: IDEATools
Type: Package
Title: R computing tools for the IDEA method
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Carayon", email = "david.carayon@irstea.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: David Carayon <david.carayon@irstea.fr>
Description: This package provides a set of tools for computing IDEA data records in an R environment.
    Functions in this package allow to extract data from IDEA4 excel files and convert them to dataframes, drawing heuristic maps and other various plots for reporting. 
